OL,5,G2340 Bradley & Barney Walsh: Breaking
OL,6,G     Dad
OL,7,     FThe Walshes are halfway through
OL,8,     Ftheir Australian road trip, and
OL,9,     Fhave reached the Gold Coast.
OL,10,     FBarney has sun, sea and some
OL,11,     Fserious action planned - starting
OL,12,     Fwith a trip to the beach, where
OL,13,     Fthey join a local outrigger canoe
OL,14,     Fclub for a race on the water.
OL,15,     FNext, the pair visit a wildlife
OL,16,     Fhospital that was set up by the
OL,17,     Fanimal-loving Steve Irwin and his
OL,18,     Ffamily. The duo also learn the art
OL,19,     Fof synchronised swimming and meet
OL,20,     Fa stunt man who has worked
OL,21,     Falongside some of Hollywood's
OL,22,     Fbiggest stars
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
